 obtain a permeability dyadic that will\ncloak magnetostatic fields. Causality conditions imply that, unlike\nmagnetostatic cloaking, electrostatic cloaking as well as low-frequency\ncloaking for w > 0 is not realizable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2007 00:05:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2007 18:47:29 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Oct 2007 21:30:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 24 Oct 2007 16:29:34 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 16 Sep 2008 01:45:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-28"}
