sired. Examples for the composed and\nthe conditional Cinderella mode for different observation setups are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2007 06:46:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2008 12:34:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-06-29"}
